title: Kill Monsters [Arcade, Eng, 2018]
description:
The portal has opened and an army of monsters has already started capturing our planet!!!
But fear not, you are a mighty warrior, destined to stop the monsters.
 
Awaiting you:

- Four heroes with unique tactics of behavior in battle and with their weapons
- 10 unique monsters
- beautiful and pleasant graphics
- an interesting open world

The Earth is in danger, and she is waiting for her HERO!

System:

ОС: Windows 7 +
CPU: 1 GHz
RAM: 128 mb
VRAM: 64 mb
HDD: 57 mb
